wiki.summary: "Adan y Eva" (english: Adam and Eve) is a song by Paulo Londra. Written by Londra himself alongside Cristian Salazar and producer Ovy on the Drums. The song went number one in Argentine, Spain, Ecuador, Peru, Costa Rica and Uruguay. In "Adan y Eva" Londra talks about wanting to do "sinful" things with his partner, just as Adam and Eve sinned. Read more on Last.fm.
